Derechos de autor (c) 2016 por Edward H. Trager. Todos los derechos reservados.
GPL v. 2.0 or later. Licencia Pública General de GNU v. 2.0 o posterior

USAGE
======
Usage: ./c2m <file to convert>

COMPILE
=======
Here is a typical command line to compile the software:

   g++ -Wall -o c2m c2m.cpp
